profile_positions.description:
-Supervising all ATAST Clubs meetings;
-Overseeing the process of the clubs' event planning;
-Overseeing all the clubs' purchase requests;
-Maintaining a current list of contact information of the ATAST Clubs presidents, advisor and members;
-Ensuring that the clubs participate in end of semester club reviews with the National board
-Holding  meetings for the general membership during the semester; 
-Reviewing all event organization requested by the ATAST Clubs;
-Following up on all the different clubs' activities.
